metadata.name: POLAROIDZ #1
metadata.description:
JPs passion for portrait photography can be seen in his third NFT collection POLAROIDZ. The collection contains 1/1 Polaroid pictures painted with markers, acrylic paint and spray paint witch make these Polaroids one of a kind. The Polaroids are also framed in a unique way using the black Polaroid cassette.

First time buyers will get the original artwork (Polaroid framed in cassette) + HIGH REZ file.
